  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "葵さんが『綺羅』のメンバーと話してた？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi-san was talking to a member of \"Kira\"?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 4.7666666985
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "うん、顔見知りみたいな雰囲気だった\nあの人、莉央さんのこと間違ってるって言ってた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ they seemed to know each other\nThat person said that Rio-san was wrong…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.2666666985,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3966.6666347999994,
          "startTime": 12.2333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 12.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 14.96
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "それって、もしかしてこの子じゃない？\nほら、このミキプロのホームページに載ってる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could it be this girl?\nLook‚ she's on this Miki Prods. homepage…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.8000013988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 20.3000015577
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう、この人！　なんですぐに分かったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right‚ this person! How did you know so fast?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.3000015577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 23.5333351453
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "こころも、その子が莉央さんと親しげに話してるのを\nつい最近見たばっかりなんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I also saw her recently talking familiarly with Rio-san\nI saw her just recently",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "……決勝トーナメント\n確かあの子のいるグループも出場が決まってたはず",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…The final tournament\nI'm sure the group that girl is in also had their participation confirmed",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 35.8000005405
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "前にも、こころ達に嫌がらせしてきた事務所の子だし\n……な～んか引っ掛かるんだよね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And she's from the agency that harassed us before\n…Some~thing feel a bit uneasy about it~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 42.5000005405
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "……そういえばあの子、気になること言ってた！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Now that I think about it‚ that girl said something that bothered me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.5000005405,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "「LizNoirもそろそろ脱落してくれそう」\n「これでもうすぐ三グループ目」って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She said 'It looks like LizNoir is about to drop out soon'\nThis makes it the third group'",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 52.5333338738
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "……ハッ！　まさかあの子……葵さんと莉央さんの\n両方に取り入って仲間割れさせるつもりじゃない！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh! Could it be that girl… is trying to cause discord\nbetween Aoi-san and Rio-san by luring them from both sides!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 59.2000028294
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "うん。まだ確信は持てないけど、リズノワは\n優勝候補の一角だし、ありえない話ではないと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I can't be sure yet‚ but LizNoir is\none of the candidates for the win and I don't think it's an unreasonable story",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 67.3333361627
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしよう！？　葵さんが脱退したり\nリズノワが解散なんてことになったら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-What should we do?! If Aoi-san withdraws\nor LizNoir disbands…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 72.9333351454
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "しかもその子が「ウチの事務所なら葵さんの\n思う通りに活動出来ますよ～」とか言い出したら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moreover‚ if that girl says‚ 'If it’s our office\nAoi-san can do whatever you want~'…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 80.8000038466
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとやめてよ、こころ。それって引き抜きじゃない\nそんなことになったら――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on‚ Kokoro. That's stealing.\nIf something like that happens――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.8666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 86.6333361627
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよ。LizNoirはおしまい\n……そうならないよう、こころ達が頑張らないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right. LizNoir is over\n…To prevent that from happening‚ we have to do our best",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 94.5333361627
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ、愛\nこのこと、莉央さんと葵さんに全部打ち明けちゃおうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Ai\nLet's tell Rio-san and Aoi-san everything about this",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 100.3000028294
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも証拠なんてないよ……\n私、あの子の独り言をたまたま聞いただけだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-But‚ we don't have any proof…\nI‚ just happened to overhear what she said to herself",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 107.6000094416
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "ああいうタイプは周到だから、証拠なんて残さないよ\n証拠探しなんてしてたら、手遅れになっちゃう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That type is meticulous‚ so she wouldn't leave any proof\nIf we waste time looking for proof‚ it'll be too late",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.9666732789,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7833.33333329999,
          "startTime": 119.8000066122
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11769.999999999996,
          "startTime": 123.7366732789
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 115.3666761083
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった。そうと決まれば早速二人にメッセを\n送っちゃおう！　「葵さん、今いいですか？」っと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Got it. If that's the case‚ I'll send a message to both of them right away\nLet's send it! 'Aoi-san‚ do you have a time now?'",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.8333399456,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10066.660054400003,
          "startTime": 129.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 121.4000066122
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 126.3333422663
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "もう二時間以上経つのに全然既読がつかない……\n仕事はだいぶ前に終わってるはずだよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's been more than two hours‚ but the message hasn't been read\nTheir work should have ended a while ago‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.1333399456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 132.1333399456
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 135.599999269
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんもだよ。二人とも、どこで何してるんだろう？\nうーん……なんだか凄～く嫌な予感がする……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Same with Rio-san. Where are they and what are they doing?\nUmm―… I have a really bad feeling about this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.5000066122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 148.6333397231
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……違う、全然戻らない……\nこんなの、僕のダンスじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ha‚ ha… No‚ it's not coming back at all…\nThis isn't my dance",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.3000025433,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3433.337402299998,
          "startTime": 163.7333399456
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "……葵？　もう練習に来てたのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Aoi? You were already here practicing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.2666811946,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "って……ちょっと貴方、ふらふらじゃない！\nオーバーワークよ。すぐに休みなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait… you're swaying a lot!\nThat's overwork. You need to rest immediately",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.6333368938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "莉央か……こんな所で何してるの？\n今日はファンサービスはしなくていいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio… what are you doing here?\nAren't you supposed to be doing fan service today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.7666702271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "……言ってくれるじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You said that",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.0666832291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "私だって、自分のパフォーマンスが\n今のままでいいなんて、全然思ってない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I‚ don't think\nmy performance is okay as it is now",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.8000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "プロモーション活動には力を入れているけど\nその分、自主練の量は増やしているわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm putting a lot of power into our promotional activities\nBut I'm increasing the amount of self-practice accordingly",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.6000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "……ねえ、莉央、今の僕達はバラバラだ\nそれなりの形にはなってるけど、見る人が見れば分かる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey Rio‚ we're apart now\nWe might look plausible‚ but a perceptive person would notice",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.5333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "このままじゃBIG4入りどころか\nデビュー前の……出会った頃の僕達に逆戻りしちゃうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we continue like this‚ instead of becoming BIG4‚\nwe'll regress back to how we were before our debut… when we first met",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.6000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "だから私は……\n貴方と一緒の練習時間が作りたくてここに来たの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why I…\nI came here because I wanted to make time to practice with you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 216.2333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "……ねぇ、葵。久しぶりに二人だけで合わせてみない？\nデビュー前の、あの頃のように",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey Aoi. For the first time in a while‚ why don't we practice just the two of us?\nLike back then‚ before our debut",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.3333257039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃は本当に楽しかった\nようやく本当のパートナーを見つけられたって思った",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was really fun back then\nI thought I had finally found my true partner",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 231.2666590373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "……貴方と私は、パートナーよ\nやってみましょう。あの頃の感覚を思い出して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You and I are partners\nLet's do it. Let's remember that feeling",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 238.7333257039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "分かったよ。それじゃ、曲は僕らのデビュー曲にしよう\n二人だった頃の",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay. Then‚ let's use our debut song\nfrom when it was just the two of us",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 249.2333246867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "いいわ。やりましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good. Let's do it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 250.8000043554,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――練習終了後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After the practice ends",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 258.8999821979,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "二人だった頃の振り付け、なんだか懐かしいわね\nあの頃が、随分昔のことに思えるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The choreography from when it was just the two of us… I miss it\nThat time feels like a long time ago",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 265.8333287555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "莉央、君はどう感じてるの？\n今の僕らを、あの頃の僕らと比べて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio‚ how do you feel about it?\nComparing us now to us back then",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 273.1666620889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "技術も体力も明らかに今の方が上よ\nでも……なくしてしまったものもある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our skills and stamina are clearly better now\nBut… there's also something we've lost",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 281.9666620889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "私達二人の間にあった一体感。そして……\n葵から湧き上がる熱気が……今の私達には、ない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The sense of unity between the two of us. And…\nthe passion that used to surge from Aoi… we don't have that now",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 291.6666620889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "うん。理由は分かってる。僕が、今のLizNoir\n――莉央のやり方に、ついていけなくなったからだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I know why. It's because I can't keep up with\n――LizNoir‚ Rio's way of doing things anymore",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 305.5666620889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ莉央。やっぱり僕は、自分らしさを、今までの\nLizNoirを捨ててまで、BIG4になりたくない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Rio. I still don't want to become BIG4\nif it means throwing away my identity and LizNoir's past",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 315.6999872842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "……私はBIG4になりたいの。こころと愛\nそして葵、貴方と四人で。だから葵、お願い……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I want to become BIG4. With Kokoro and Ai\nand also Aoi‚ with the four of us. So Aoi‚ please…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 325.2333175658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "久しぶりに莉央と二人で練習して、初心を思い出せば\n気持ちが変わるかもしれない、なんて思ったんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought that if I practiced with Rio alone after a long time‚\nand remembered our beginnings‚ my feelings might change",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 337.7666529337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "……やっぱりそんな訳ないよね\n……莉央、僕は決勝トーナメントには出ない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That can’t be happening\n…Rio‚ I'm not going to participate in the final tournament",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 348.799986267,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirは三人で出場してほしい\nその方が勝算があるよ。それと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want LizNoir to participate with just the three of you\nThat way‚ you'll have a better chance of winning. And…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 356.199986267,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "僕がLizNoirの活動を休止することを\n許してほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please allow me to take a break\nfrom LizNoir activities",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 365.199986267,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "――っ！　そんなの、許せる訳ないじゃない！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――! There's no way I could allow something like that!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 366.5999890963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_05-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "莉央はBIG4に――トップアイドルになるんでしょ？\nなら、そろそろ捨てる覚悟を決めるべきだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio is going to be BIG4―― a top idol‚ right?\nThen‚ it's time for you to prepare to throw away something",
